  "prompt": "Is native advertising the future of online advertising?",
  "response": "Native advertising has become increasingly important in online advertising, but opinions vary on whether it will completely replace traditional ad formats. Some advantages of native advertising include:\n\n1. Better user experience\n2. Higher engagement rates\n3. Less disruptive than traditional display ads\n4. More seamless integration with content\n\nHowever, challenges include maintaining transparency and avoiding deceptive practices. While native advertising is likely to continue growing, a diverse advertising ecosystem with multiple formats is probably more realistic than a single approach.",
